      :EndIf
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźConnect datasource;src;opt
      SQA.Init''
      :If 0=‚äÉsrc‚ÜźSQA.DSN''
          src‚Üź2‚äÉsrc          ‚ćĚ List of available ODBC data sources
      :Else
          ‚éēSIGNAL‚äā('EN' 500)('Vendor' 'DCMS')('Message'(2‚äÉsrc))   ‚ćĚ Error getting ODBC data sources
      :EndIf
      :If ~(1‚Ć∑datasource)‚ąä‚ć•‚éēC‚ä£/src
          'opt'‚éēNS ‚ć¨ ‚čĄ opt.(wait timeout)‚Üź3 5 ‚čĄ opt.datasource‚Üź‚äÉdatasource
          Reconnect opt
      :EndIf
      :If 0‚Č†‚äÉr‚ÜźSQA.Connect db,‚ć•‚äÜdatasource
          :If 10009=2‚äÉr
              ‚éē‚Üź'Already connected to ',‚äÉdatasource
          :Else
              ‚éē‚Üźr
              ‚éēSIGNAL‚äā('EN'(‚äÉr))('Vendor' 'DCMS')('Message'('Could not connect to ',‚äÉdatasource))
          :EndIf
      :EndIf
      ‚éē‚ÜźDo'create database if not exists dyalog_cms'
      ‚éē‚ÜźUse'dyalog_cms'
      ‚éē‚Üź'Connected to SQL database: ',‚äÉdatasource
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźReconnect opt;src;timeout;found
      :Repeat
          Catch ¬Į1 'Attempting to find datasource ',opt.datasource,‚äā'. ',(‚ćēopt.wait),' attempts remaining.'
          ‚éēDL opt.timeout
          Catch src‚ÜźSQA.DSN'' ‚čĄ src‚Üź2‚äÉsrc
          found‚Üź(1‚Ć∑datasource)‚ąä‚ć•‚éēC‚ä£/src
          opt.wait-‚Üź1 ‚čĄ timeout‚Üźopt.wait‚Č§0
      :Until timeout‚ą®found
      ‚éēSIGNAL‚äā('EN' 500)('Vendor' 'DCMS')('Message'('Datasource ',(‚äÉdatasource),' not found.'))
    ‚ąá

    ‚ąá r‚ÜźUse database
