    ‚ąá r‚ÜźDoBulk(sql values);bulk;nulls;n
      n‚Üź‚ČĘ‚äÉ‚ć£(1=‚ČĘ‚ćīvalues)‚äĘvalues
      r‚ÜźCatch SQA.Prepare cur sql('Bulk'n)
      r‚ÜźCatch SQA.X cur{2=‚ČĘ‚ćī‚ćĶ:‚ćļ ‚ćĶ ‚čĄ ‚ćļ‚äā‚ćõ,‚ćĶ}values   ‚ćĚ Allows SQAPL nulls matrix to be optionally provided stranded with values
      r‚ÜźCatch SQA.Close cur
